{"tid":991652,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「好奇一問」我喺越南見到呢啲女人","createTime":"2019-01-22T13:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T05:23:14.000Z","uid":231598,"like":23,"dislike":202,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb87fa8b57d4254b33897b4f3263215847048ad","tid":991652,"uid":231598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"喺胡志明步行街見到啲按摩女郎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6H7eJNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6H7eJNc.png&h=1c27fc57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSor唔敢直接影所以個人好細粒<br />\n<br />\n想問兩個問題：<br />\n1. 其實佢地純粹喺門口拉客入去按<br />\n定佢地真係會幫你按（我睇又唔似）<br />\n<br />\n2. 其實佢地係真係按摩定係有啲特別服務<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心想知<br />\n知答案嘅巴打可唔可以解答下<br />\n<br />\n我頭先自己一個行過<br />\n俾一個捉住左，我好驚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，想分享張唯美貼圖<br />\n想大家純粹欣賞下越南女仔<br />\n個人覺得佢都都幾吸引<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19jMzVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19jMzVC.png&h=069ec6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家唔好起邪念，Thz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aa06420627007d7a7eeed14027a1764cacbdd1","tid":991652,"uid":12208,"like":103,"dislike":8,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"好多白滑淫腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a400d4ba22ef22a2f188ab3223cd0d53dbcd4a","tid":991652,"uid":46042,"like":75,"dislike":4,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"全國做雞"},{"pid":"96b843282abbd6777b3144a41776d2690abcbb70","tid":991652,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89d